    public class CNUStdImgFile
extends DisplayComponent
implements iiVScriptable, CNUFileObject, java.lang.Cloneable
    CNUStdImgFile creates a displayable object from standard 2d image formats supported by CNUFile.
    Since:
    iiV1.0
    See Also:
